### Circuito completo de pujas. Usar con la extension REST Client de VS Code
### o IntelliJ HTTP Client. Ejecutar en orden.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1) Login (Juan, categoria oro)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "juan@email.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Guardar el token devuelto
@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### 2) Listar subastas abiertas
GET {{host}}/api/subastas?estado=abierta
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) Items de la subasta 50 (plata, ARS)
GET {{host}}/api/subastas/50/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Oferta actual del item 1 (Reloj, base 1000, Maria pujo 1500)
GET {{host}}/api/subastas/50/items/1/oferta-actual
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) Unirse a la subasta 50
POST {{host}}/api/clientes/me/unirse
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "subastaId": 50 }

### 6) Pujar 1600 (valida: min = 1500 + 1% de 1000 = 1510, max = 1500 + 20% = 1700)
POST {{host}}/api/subastas/50/items/1/pujas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "importe": 1600 }

### 6b) Puja invalida (muy baja) -> 409 PUJA_TOO_LOW
POST {{host}}/api/subastas/50/items/1/pujas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "importe": 1505 }

### 6c) Puja invalida (supera el 20%) -> 409 PUJA_TOO_HIGH
POST {{host}}/api/subastas/50/items/1/pujas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "importe": 1800 }

### 7) Mis pujas
GET {{host}}/api/clientes/me/pujas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) Mi perfil
GET {{host}}/api/clientes/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) Mis medios de pago
GET {{host}}/api/clientes/me/metodos-pago
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10) Notificaciones
GET {{host}}/api/clientes/me/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
